flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Annual planning cycle initiation or significant market changes.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Extract historical spend data from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Analyze historical spend data and market intelligence reports.]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: AutoML - Evaluate supplier performance metrics and internal capability assessments.]
  N3 --> N4{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Develop annual indirect spend plan and category strategies.}
  N4 -->|Primary| N5[PB: Remote Functions - Finalize and approve the indirect spend plan and strategies.]
  N5 --> N6[UI: UI Screens - Surface the approved plan and strategies on a dashboard.]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced indirect COGS, improved cash conversion, and alignment of strategic spend with supplier capabilities and market benchmarks.]
  N4 -->|Significant market changes detected.| B1[Trigger re-evaluation of market intelligence and budget allocation.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Adjust indirect spend plan and strategies accordingly.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Supplier performance metrics indicate...| B2[Initiate supplier performance improvement actions.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Enhance supplier capabilities and terms.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Internal capability assessments sugge...| B3[Recommend internal sourcing options.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Optimize total cost of ownership and reduce external sourcing risk.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]